latestPosts.caption:
🥹✨11.01.25!✨🥹

I was numb! I am still numb! I still can’t believe the number, am I dreaming?💭😟 Because I have never dreamt of this particular number when I first started this journey!😅So still processing...
 
I was travelling on the train when my mother called & started shouting, “mona 1million hoye gachhe!!” & it felt like board exam ar result beriyechhe! 😁😃Yes, I am an emotional person so I cried, I cried especially when @_myself_riya & Shakib gave me the surprise on the platform🫂, I cried when my family surprised me 🥹🤗, I went to my previous room where I started this journey n I cried again! 🥹🫶

You guys are asking for a grand celebration! But I really don’t know how to do it! Because at heart I am still that small town girl & she doesn’t know how to celebrate, where to celebrate these 10lakh people!!!! 

So all ideas are welcome!👐 & One more thing I know you guys have lots of questions for me, so shoot them in the comments🔫. I will make a QnA video for you guys to answer them!💕 Till then let me process this number...🥹🥹🫶🫶
————————————

Image 2: A real ‘Surprise’ from family!😁💕🤗

Image 5: Ador r adorrrrrr😘😘😘
